Class Weather

  • java.lang.Object
    • Weather

  • public class Weather
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates a weather condition for the frog to struggle with during the game. In this implementation, the weather is a form of lightning that paralyzes the frog momentarily
    Version:
    May 21, 2016
    Author:
    Uday Tripathi, Period: 5, Assignment: Frogger Final Project, Sources: None
